Suspected bandits have kidnapped the wife and son of Almustapha Danmusa, the head of administration, Mani Local Government Area of Katsina State. The abduction was said to have been carried out on Sunday night by bandits in their house at Dandagoro residential area.  However, SaharaReporters learned that the kidnappers had contacted the family of the victims and demanded N5 million for their release. 